cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with the problem of out-of-distribution detection in image classification using neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper discusses the theoretical analysis of the proposed method, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
